data.description: Your property search can end here with this meticulously maintained home. Built in 2022, this home is 1842 square feet and boasts four spacious bedrooms with a split floor plan, two full bathrooms and a two car garage. The large primary bedroom hosts a large bathroom with double sinks, linen storage, split closets, large soaking tub and a gorgeous walk-in shower. Kitchen offers plenty of storage and counter space with a large walk-in pantry. Storage space was not taken lightly when this home was built with oversized closets and overhead cabinetry in the laundry room. This home includes double spray foam insulation in the attic.
